Non-Functional Requirements 
• Application responsiveness with a 300 millisecond response time. 
• User data must be stored securely. 
• Compliance with WCAG 2.1 accessibility standards. 
• Reliable accessibility with minimal downtime. 
• Responsive design optimized for phones and tablets.
